{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "The objective of this course is to investigate the social rules, both discernible and hidden, which govern everyday activities in Japan. In the course students will learn about the value systems which underlie Japanese behavior and perception and by doing so will uncover what would be considered pragmatically appropriate within particular contexts.", "到達目標": "Students will gain knowledge of Japanese social structures and social behavior. They will be able to ask critical questions about Japanese behavior. They will be able to explain pragmatic differences between their own culture and that of Japan. They will be able to analyze behavior and opinions in order to uncover the hidden values associated with them. They will be able to conduct thoughtful discussion of the class readings. They will be able to make clear presentations and/or reports on assigned topics.", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "This course will be conducted in English only and English will be the means of communication between the students and the instructor.  (Students will also be expected to communicate with one another in English.)\nStudents are encouraged to actively participate in class discussions, both independently and collaboratively.", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm;font-size:medium;font-family:Cambria,serif;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\">【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\">Startup Week</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\">】リンク：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;color:rgb(238,0,0);\">https://</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;color:rgb(238,0,0);\">********(to be provided by the instructor later)</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"